runs.comm: short of a good length outside off, chopped down behind point for a single
punched to midwicket off the back foot
shortish outside off, moving away, tries to poke at it and misses
edged, moved away after landing on the off stump, tried to defend it off the back foot, it flew off the outside edge past point for a single
nicely dealt with, banged in short on middle, got into position early and pulled it away over square leg for a boundary
good length on the off, gets forward and defends it to cover
doles out a full delivery outside off, lands in the slot and Chibhabha creams it through the covers
short of a good length and it gets it to nip away, Chibabha slashes hard but can't connect
getting some shape is Aldridge, Chibhabha charges down the track and tries to drive him through the covers but can't get hold
short and he seized the length early, rocked back and pulled it hard over mid-on
goes all the way, banged in short on middle, goes for the pull over square leg, comes onto him a little quickly, gets a top edge that carries the ball over the fine-leg boundary
good length, punched firmly but straight to extra cover, an expensive start for Aldridge
Zimbabwe have started well here, dropped it short on the off, he moved away and hammered him over mid-on
gone! Nicely bowled by Bracewell, angled in, landed in the channel outside off and moved away, Masakadza tried to open the face and got a feather on it, McCullum made no mistake
short outside off, guided uppishly towards third man for a single
quick, bowled it short on middle, ducked under it and let it be
shortish outside off, chopped it wide of slip for a single
short of a good length, dropped it short in front of cover, no single on offer there
angled in, good length on middle, tries to hit him through the line, gets an inside edge onto the pads
full outside off, on a length, tries to smash him down the ground but makes no contact
short on middle, comes down the track and tries to pull him square, misses, good comeback from Aldridge this
bowled him with the slower one, changed his pace, Taylor tried to swing him over midwicket a little too early, didn't pick the slower one and lost his middle stump, Zimbabwe in trouble
full outside off, pitched up and he drives it nicely past extra cover for three runs, Chigumbura starts off in fine fashion
length ball and he goes after it, lofts it over the bowler's head for a boundary, a couple of bounces before rolled over
good length on the off, opts to play it off the back foot, defends it to cover
shortish on the off, drops it towards point from the crease
banged it short and he picked it late, went for the pull, was struck on the neck after he missed out on the pull, nothing serious though, he's on his feet
very nicely timed, bowled it full on middle and he chipped it over mid-on, had enough on it to take it to the boundary
short outside off and he gears up for the pull but fails to connect
smashed, goes all the way, slower one bowled full on the off, he picked it off a length, straight over the long-off boundary, middled it well
short of a good length on middle, run down towards point
nicely placed, short of a good length, opened the face and guided it really fine to beat third man to the boundary
short and it's hammered hard off the back foot to bisect the gap between deep cover and deep point
quicker from Oram, short of a good length, hurried past Chigumbura who tried to reach that one
slower one bowled short, cut away uppishly past point for a couple into the deep
nipped back in, tried to chop it into the off side, got an inside edge behind the keeper for a couple more
tossed up on middle, driven down to long-on for a single
driven hard towards long-off for one more
superbly done, charged down the track, was slightly flighed and he made his mind up, came down and smacked it over the bowler's head
quicker through the air, shortish on middle, defended into the off side
shortish, comes down the track and punches it to extra cover
flighted on middle, pushed back firmly to the bowler
shortish on middle, strikes him on the thigh as he tries to work that away sneaks a leg-bye
short of a good length on middle, fends it into the leg side
short outside off, cut away towards third man for a single
banged it short down the leg side, called a wide
fullish on middle, hits it through the line to long-on, just the single
slower one bowled short on the off, turned to midwicket, tidy over this
nicely timed, short on the off, made a bit of room and punched it past extra cover for a couple of runs, good fielding in the deep
attacks Woodcock, steps out of his crease and deposits him miles over wide long-on
tighter, on middle and leg, slightly shorter, played back to the bowler
made room and chopped it behind point for a couple of runs
finds the gap, a long hop from Woodcock, dropped it earlly short, made room and slapped it over extra cover for four more
punched wide of extra cover but can't quite beat the fielder
goes for the sweep, landed outside leg and spun in, missed it as he tried to hit it past square leg
pitched up from round the wicket on the off stump, pushed to extra cover
short outside off, chopped it wide of point for a single
superb reaction, low full toss and it's driven back, he's alert and dives to his left and low to pluck it inches from the ground, was a clean catch, Chigumbura has to go
goodish length on the off, played towards extra cover

Zimbabwe back in trouble, the ball stopped on him there, landed around a good length, Coventry came forward to play it into the leg side but was caught surprised as it stopped on him, ended up lobbing it wide of the bowler, he ran a few paces to his right and snapped it easily with his right hand
full toss on the off, pushed past McCullum to long-on for a single
flighted on middle, pushed down to long-on for a single
cleanly struck, tossed up and Chibhabha senses a chance, dances down the track and gets to the pitch before sending it over long-off
turned past square leg for a single
pushed past extra cover into the deep for a couple of runs
punched straight to extra cover this time
full toss on middle, pushed down to long-on for a single
fires it quick outside off, sliced to deep cover for a single
shortish on leg stump, turned wide of square leg for one more
full toss, pulled away straight to Franklin at deep midwicket on the bounce
short on middle, punched off the back foot past extra cover, it's nicely timed, all they can manage is a couple though
guided wide of point for a single
dug out into the leg side, fired into the blockhole
yorker on middle, well bowled, dug out back to the bowler
bowled full on the off, drilled hard but straight to long-off for a single
slower one bowled full outside off, driven down the ground to long-off
low full toss on the off, played down to long-on, Nathan McCullum fumbles in the deep to allow them the second
nicely placed, there is a short third man and a point in place and he finds the gap, slicing that slower one between those two fielders. Half-century as well for Chibhabha
full on the off, driven hard to deep cover for a single to keep strike
he's struck the ball superbly today, pitched up by McCullum on middle, stood his ground and thwacked it over the bowler's head for a flat six
pushed towards long-off for a single
dug out into the leg side
slower through the air this time, lands full outside off and he drags it handsomely over the wide long-on boundary

stumped, that one was fired in outside off and it didn't turn, Chibhabha hopped out of the track to play it into the off side, he expected it to turn but it didn't, missed and Brendon McCullum did the rest
slightly short outside off, pushed past point for a single
shortish outside off, cut down to third man for a single
dropped by Bracewell, was the slower one, tried to swing it over midwicket, got a leading edge and Bracewell at short third tried to take it running back but couldn't hold on
sweetly struck, full toss and it's struck meatily over midwicket to beat Nathan McCullum at long-on
yorker length, dug out into the leg side towards long-on for a single
found the gap, slower one bowled full outside off, made a bit of room and crashed it through extra cover for a boundary
aiming for the blockhole, pushed wide of long-on and completes the second in time
full toss from Oram, whipped away hard past square leg for a boundary, tough chance for Bracewell there and he didn't get his body behind it
slower one bowled short outside leg stump, goes for the pull, clips his thighs and McCullum does well to  get some body behind that, just the single in the end
Zimbabwe are putting up a fight, slower one bowled short outside off, cut away over point for a boundary
Waller has to go, full toss outside off, smashed but straight to Ross Taylor at extra cover
goes for the paddle, tries to scoop him over short fine, is struck on the pads
short on middle, pulled to deep midwicket, just the single
low full toss, whipped away to deep square leg for a single

good length on middle, pulls it hard over square leg but can't find the ropes, there's confusion in the middle and it's a good throw from Oram in the deep, McCullum collects well and takes down the stumps to find Mutizwa well short, run-out

shortish on middle, pulled to midwicket, both want the single but Utseya backs out at the last moment and runs back, Price has run halfway down the pitch by then, it's an easy run-out at the striker's end
gone! It's a team hat-trick for New Zealand, short of a good length on the off, makes room does Jarvis and feathers it to the keeper, three wickets in three balls
four wickets in four balls, it's all over, good length ball and he tries to go over the top on the leg side, gets a leading edge towards third man and Aldridge there makes no mistake
